00:49:34.596 --> 00:49:35.597
L.

769
00:49:40.686 --> 00:49:41.687
O.

770
00:49:46.108 --> 00:49:47.943
V.

771
00:49:48.026 --> 00:49:49.027
Love.

772
00:49:53.407 --> 00:49:55.492
I miss him so much.

773
00:50:00.664 --> 00:50:03.083
I love you too. Dominic.

774
