802
00:51:41.890 --> 00:51:44.142
Give me my shit. dude. G… give me my shit.

803
00:51:44.226 --> 00:51:47.187
-Yeah. we have problems.
-Why are you trying to torment me?

804
00:51:47.270 --> 00:51:49.940
-We have problems.
-You're trying to torment me.

805
00:52:05.122 --> 00:52:07.791
This was clearly a toxic relationship

806
00:52:07.874 --> 00:52:12.420
