810
00:52:32.149 --> 00:52:33.942
But two weeks before the crash.

811
00:52:34.025 --> 00:52:37.988
Dominic's mother. Christine Russo.
received a telephone call from her son.

812
00:52:38.071 --> 00:52:43.994
